   It is not yet known with certainty how long COVID-19 can stay on the surface of an object, although preliminary studies show that COVID-19 can last for several hours, depending on the type of surface, temperature, or humidity of the environment. But a simple disinfectant can kill the virus so that it is impossible to infect people again. And familiarize hand washing with soap and water, or alcohol-based hand rub, and avoid touching your eyes, mouth or nose (facial triangle) more effectively protect yourself.
